1
command to add user account: sudo adduser sam, sudo adduser joe, sudo adduser amy, sudo adduser sara, sudo adduser admin

2
command to edit pwquality.conf file:sudo nano pwquality.conf
updates to configuration file : changes required characters to 16 with at least 1 number and 1 symbol

3
command to set each new users password to expire in 90 days:sudo chage -M 90 sam, sudo chage -M 90 joe, sudo chage -M 90 amy, sudo chage -M 90 sara, sudo chage -M 90 admin

4
command to add admin to the sudo group: sudo usermod -aG sudo admin
